-- Roubini Says China Should Allow Gradual Yuan Rise, Support Domestic Demand
-- B y   R a n j e e t h a   P a k i a m
-- 2010-09-27T03:09:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-27/roubini-says-china-should-allow-gradual-yuan-rise-support-domestic-demand.html
China should allow for the gradual
appreciation of its currency, New York University Professor
Nouriel Roubini said in Kuala Lumpur today.  Emerging economies may have to get used to relying on
domestic demand in a period of anemic economic growth for
advanced nations, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
